page.title: 01OVERVIEW OF WEST FLEGG AREA
page.content: { {44,17}The B1152 runs through this square.There are some buildings on the side of the B1152.{44,16}The A149 runs through this part & at the end are houses & a public house.{44,15}Lots of little lanes & some lovely views.{ {45,17}The B1152 runs along the edge.At the end there are houses,a post office & a church.There are some more back lanes {45,16}There are lots of lanes & houses.On the corner there is the A149.{45,15}By the side of the A149 there is a playing field & a Primary school next door.At the back the views are of fields and houses.There is a broad.{ORMESBY 46,17 46,16 46,15 47,17 {47,16 47,15}there are lots of lanes & tracks hardly any marsh land some broads also some woodland it is very quiet & peaceful.
